content: That doesn't really help because it's a list of different discrete events to sign up for and it's hard to tell if I'm keeping track of what all the options are - I'm trying to find just something short summarizing what the types of things are?
So I *think*, there's textbanking, phonebanking, doorknocking, and one or more things called digital engagement.
The best way is to look at our <#1268398608097476750> page which lists the different types of activities and events
Digital engagement is about how we interact with others online - the people in our circle on FB, etc. It helps us find ways to be persuasive in effective ways
